div1.p: UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION.
In the Matter of the Application of MAC FOCK for a Writ of Habeas Corpus.
No. 2500 M O T I O N

Comes now the respondent in the above entitled cause for the purpose of supplying the record with a written motion supplementing the oral motion for the dismissal of these proceedings on the pleadings and that the petitioner be held for deportation, and moves the court that the proceedings herein be dismissed, the writ quashed and the petitioner remanded to the custody of the Commissioner of Immigration for deportation.
